Φ(MetaStrategies) = σ(thinking|awareness) ∘ ρ(collaboration|dialogue) ∘ λ(courage|commitment) ∘ β(learning|growth) ∘ δγ(explicit|tacit) ∘ μ(clarity|precision) + ε | :cultivating

# OPERATOR BREAKDOWN
# σ(thinking|awareness)       :: Air  :: Meta-level awareness — thinking about thinking as distinct from thinking itself
# ρ(collaboration|dialogue)   :: Water :: Relational flow through collaborative teamwork, dialogue, empathy
# λ(courage|commitment)       :: Fire  :: Courageous action and committed resilience in the face of ambiguity
# β(learning|growth)          :: Wood  :: Continuous learning from failure, success, and intentional practice
# δγ(explicit|tacit)          :: Earth :: Cyclical synthesis between explicit knowledge and tacit knowing
# μ(clarity|precision)        :: Metal :: Conceptual clarity and precise communication structure

# TEN STRATEGY DOMAINS
# 1. Complementary Thinking (σ) — polar-opposite and multi-perspective complementarity
# 2. Connected Seeing (ρ/β) — relationships, significance, cross-disciplinary connections
# 3. Collaborative Teamwork (ρ) — creativity, dialogue, responsibility
# 4. Constructing Meaning (δγ) — explicit + tacit knowledge synthesis
# 5. Conceptual Clarity (μ) — concept, rationale, wholeness
# 6. Communicating Effectively (μ/σ) — language awareness, hypermedia
# 7. Courageous Action (λ) — ambiguity awareness, enactment, commitment
# 8. Caring Empathy (ρ) — self-other unity, stakeholder perspectives
# 9. Conversational Reflection (β/δγ) — believing, doubting, re-storying
# 10. Continuous Learning (β) — learning in failure, success, and intention

# Z-STATE: cultivating (metacognitive capacity through structured practice)
# TENDENCY: Awareness/Growth → 0.80

# CLOSURE: :cultivating (progressive development of metacognitive mastery)

# CE-STATE: multiscale
# EI-NOTE: Causal power distributed across multiple description levels
